To install vim settings on a machine:
1. Register the ssh keys of the new machine: https://help.github.com/articles/generating-ssh-keys/
2. Once ssh is setup:
    cd ~
    git clone http://github.com/ashwinaj/vim.git ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
